1
00:00:01,200 --> 00:00:02,996
T-O-J?

2
00:00:02,996 --> 00:00:05,519
This competition is organised to select
Japan's top high school student.

3
00:00:05,519 --> 00:00:08,508
If she wins, you'll allow her to continue her
association with Tsukasa,

4
00:00:08,508 --> 00:00:11,538
and you will also stop harassing Makino.

5
00:00:11,538 --> 00:00:13,463
It's not worth gambling for.

6
00:00:13,463 --> 00:00:14,609
I'll help sharpen you.

7
00:00:14,609 --> 00:00:15,580
We will all be beside you.

8
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:17,338
I told you that if something happens,
you can always come to me for help.

9
00:00:17,338 --> 00:00:20,970
