10
00:00:20,970 --> 00:00:24,182
It's because of your mom that so many
innocent people got involved.

11
00:00:24,182 --> 00:00:26,783
If we, the F4, are on your side,
what's there to be afraid of?

12
00:00:26,783 --> 00:00:28,393
Just be yourself and do it.

13
00:00:29,366 --> 00:00:30,467
