18
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:49,583
We now have the participants of Teen of Japan 2005,

19
00:00:49,563 --> 00:00:52,553
who will fight for the title of Japan's Top High School Student.

20
00:00:54,693 --> 00:00:56,475
It's Tsukushi!
Tsukushi!

21
00:00:56,475 --> 00:00:58,958
