27
00:01:15,059 --> 00:01:18,401
What's the relationship between that pretty girl
and Tsukasa?

28
00:01:18,401 --> 00:01:20,455
She's Tsukasa's fiance.

29
00:01:20,455 --> 00:01:21,388
Fiance?

30
00:01:21,388 --> 00:01:23,722
Tsukushi!

31
00:01:23,722 --> 00:01:26,282
<Do your best!!
Makino Tsukushi>

32
00:01:39,031 --> 00:01:41,250
You b*stards, what are you going to do with me?

33
00:01:41,242 --> 00:01:43,127
I'm sorry, Young Master. Please calm down.

34
00:01:43,127 --> 00:01:46,000
Nishida, what's the meaning of this?!

35
00:01:45,995 --> 00:01:47,445
It hurts...!

36
00:01:47,445 --> 00:01:55,042
Next, we have the main judge of TOJ,
Yamanaka Minako to start the competition.

37
00:01:55,023 --> 00:01:58,868
I hope that all the participants will be able to display

38
00:01:58,868 --> 00:02:04,258
their beauty, knowledge, and homemaking skills,
as much as possible.

39
00:02:04,258 --> 00:02:08,897
Teen of Japan 2005 will now begin!

40
00:02:16,078 --> 00:02:20,625
This year's competition will be slightly different
from the previous years.

41
00:02:20,632 --> 00:02:23,569
Previously, there were 3 categories for judging.

42
00:02:23,569 --> 00:02:25,265
But this year, there will be four.

43
00:02:25,265 --> 00:02:30,320
The first challenge for everyone is...

44
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,935
A talent show.

45
00:02:31,935 --> 00:02:36,510
You have only one minute to perform.
Please show the audience what you do best.

46
00:02:36,510 --> 00:02:38,803
It just started, and it's already a surprise.

47
00:02:38,803 --> 00:02:42,184
Please take the next 30 seconds to prepare.

48
00:02:42,184 --> 00:02:44,542
Hey hey, I didn't hear about this.

49
00:02:46,585 --> 00:02:49,351
Alright!

50
00:02:50,814 --> 00:02:55,083
Before the results came out, Ma'am wanted to make sure...

51
00:02:55,097 --> 00:02:57,544
