52
00:03:19,983 --> 00:03:21,956
Yuriko!

53
00:03:38,786 --> 00:03:41,184
Sanjyo Sakurako isn't bad.

54
00:03:41,184 --> 00:03:44,722
Being young is still the best after all.

55
00:03:44,722 --> 00:03:46,272
That's not what I meant.

56
00:03:52,165 --> 00:03:54,249
This is bad...

57
00:03:54,249 --> 00:03:56,744
What should I do?

58
00:04:00,078 --> 00:04:02,011
Next, Makino Tsukushi-san!

59
00:04:02,352 --> 00:04:04,207
You're the third one.

60
00:04:08,562 --> 00:04:12,333
That isn't too nice, forcefully bringing Tsukasa
back at a time like this.

61
00:04:13,184 --> 00:04:16,334
Anyway, she'll never win.

62
00:04:17,018 --> 00:04:19,662
The only person who thinks that way is you.

63
00:04:26,744 --> 00:04:29,098
Hey hey, what's Makino up to?

64
00:04:29,098 --> 00:04:33,917
I've decided to demonstrate to everyone
how to deal with perverts.

65
00:04:35,889 --> 00:04:38,368
