the top high school student.

66
00:04:38,368 --> 00:04:40,917
Not really, it could be very interesting.

67
00:04:40,917 --> 00:04:42,520
Please go ahead.

68
00:04:51,216 --> 00:04:52,173
Wait a minute!

69
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:05,833
Tsukasa has changed a lot ever since
he started the relationship with Tsukushi.

70
00:05:07,634 --> 00:05:10,674
What exactly do you mean?

71
00:05:10,674 --> 00:05:15,100
Tsukasa truly likes Tsukushi.

72
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:18,214
He became more gentleman-like because of his love for Tsukushi,

73
00:05:18,214 --> 00:05:23,015
even though he usually doesn't care about other people's feelings.

74
00:05:25,546 --> 00:05:27,958
Okka High, Nakazawa Atsuka-san.

75
00:05:29,574 --> 00:05:32,328
Eiri High, Kurimaki Ayano-san.

76
00:05:32,328 --> 00:05:33,201
Here.

77
00:05:33,806 --> 00:05:37,659
Eitoku High, Sanjyo Sakurako-san.

78
00:05:37,659 --> 00:05:39,618
All the great things about Tsukushi,

79
00:05:39,618 --> 00:05:42,475
you are the only one who hasn't realised them.

80
00:05:43,138 --> 00:05:46,566
Eitoku High, Makino Tsukushi-san.

81
00:05:50,479 --> 00:05:55,583
It's necessary for every modern independent woman
to know how to defend herself against perverts.

82
00:05:55,591 --> 00:05:56,714
Great!

83
00:05:56,714 --> 00:05:58,363
Way to go!

84
00:05:58,363 --> 00:05:59,536
Yes!

85
00:06:04,569 --> 00:06:05,225
<First Category>

86
00:06:05,225 --> 00:06:07,601
Tsubaki-san, be careful of your stand.

87
00:06:12,059 --> 00:06:16,147
If that girl wins,

88
00:06:17,097 --> 00:06:20,041
I'll seriously consider whatever you've said.

89
00:06:21,238 --> 00:06:24,034
However, if she doesn't win...

90
00:06:25,796 --> 00:06:28,034
That's reality for you...

91
00:06:30,439 --> 00:06:31,705
Ma'am.

92
00:06:38,338 --> 00:06:39,631
Tsukasa.

93
00:06:39,631 --> 00:06:41,766
Tsubaki-san, you leave first.

94
00:06:44,789 --> 00:06:51,562
If I didn't do this, he'd never listen to me.

95
00:06:57,350 --> 00:07:00,917
Next, we have the Beauty category.

96
00:07:00,911 --> 00:07:03,750
Please select your choice of clothing from those available,

97
00:07:03,737 --> 00:07:06,118
and then display your style to everyone.

98
00:07:06,118 --> 00:07:07,990
A time challenge?

99
00:07:07,990 --> 00:07:11,583
That girl might win, since she's really good
at getting bargains when buying clothes.

100
00:07:11,567 --> 00:07:14,046
Yep. She often goes to the local store to get them.

101
00:07:14,046 --> 00:07:17,224
But those are all branded clothes from the Paris Collection.

102
00:07:17,224 --> 00:07:18,699
Paris Collection?

103
00:07:19,699 --> 00:07:21,872
You have 3 minutes to make your selection.

104
00:07:21,872 --> 00:07:25,231
Please proceed backstage to change after you are done.

105
00:07:25,231 --> 00:07:28,046
Well then, please begin now.

106
00:07:33,022 --> 00:07:35,246
You can't expect less of Ayano, it's like she's used to this.

107
00:07:35,246 --> 00:07:37,583
Those are nothing to her.

108
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:40,365
Makino seems very lost.

109
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:48,749
Which one is good?

110
00:07:49,561 --> 00:07:53,000
Hey! There isn't all the time in the world!

111
00:07:55,275 --> 00:07:57,641
Not good...

112
00:07:58,411 --> 00:07:59,820
Heck, this one then.

113
00:08:01,422 --> 00:08:02,872
Why do you intend to do?

114
00:08:05,271 --> 00:08:07,755
I will protect Makino no matter what.

115
00:08:07,755 --> 00:08:13,458
Ayano-chan is there. So she has no chance of winning.

116
00:08:15,761 --> 00:08:18,849
Makino is the type who will always do her best
no matter what cirumstances she is in.

117
00:08:18,849 --> 00:08:22,974
Well then, if Makino is unable to win...

118
00:08:25,138 --> 00:08:29,894
If she doesn't win, you must do as I say.

119
00:08:31,123 --> 00:08:33,050
Makino, congratulations.

120
00:08:35,061 --> 00:08:36,436
Thanks.

121
00:08:36,436 --> 00:08:39,491
If you win this, you'll be able to get the approval of

122
00:08:39,491 --> 00:08:42,506
Domyoji's mom to let you and him continue your relationship.

123
00:08:43,114 --> 00:08:46,185
It's not really because of that...

124
00:08:46,185 --> 00:08:49,887
The whole of Eitoku High knows about it.

125
00:08:49,887 --> 00:08:54,958
I've got to do my best, since I'm representing Eitoku High.

126
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,134
Umm...

127
00:09:02,108 --> 00:09:04,503
Sorry. I've never greeted you properly before.

128
00:09:04,503 --> 00:09:06,817
My name is Kurimaki Ayano.

129
00:09:06,817 --> 00:09:10,458
Ah. I'm Makino Tsukushi. Nice to meet you.

130
00:09:10,449 --> 00:09:12,444
I know this might be a bit impolite,

131
00:09:12,444 --> 00:09:15,229
what's going on between you and Tsukasa?

132
00:09:15,229 --> 00:09:17,750
Right now, she's the one that Domyoji-san loves.

133
00:09:18,847 --> 00:09:22,078
Ah... No... I...

134
00:09:22,078 --> 00:09:23,658
Eh?!

135
00:09:27,407 --> 00:09:31,730
If she does win, I'll agree to whatever you say.

136
00:09:32,246 --> 00:09:39,375
Otherwise, you must listen to me.

137
00:09:39,394 --> 00:09:41,530
Any problems?

138
00:09:49,394 --> 00:09:51,700
Are you alright, Makino-san?

139
00:09:53,420 --> 00:10:00,250
That girl can go ahead and win, and everything will be fine.

140
00:10:11,909 --> 00:10:15,756
Really... Unbelievable...

141
00:10:15,953 --> 00:10:24,250
Hana Yori Dango - Boys Over Flowers
Episode 9 - Season Finale

142
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:28,417
Timing and Translation ** Backalley

