145
00:10:41,195 --> 00:10:45,083
Next we have... Kurimaki Ayano-san.

146
00:10:56,547 --> 00:10:58,398
She lives up to her name.

147
00:10:58,398 --> 00:11:01,329
Did you like her previously?

148
00:11:02,291 --> 00:11:04,312
I'm really right?

149
00:11:04,864 --> 00:11:07,742
D*mmit...

150
00:11:12,371 --> 00:11:15,651
Makino-san from Eitoku High, please get ready.

151
00:11:15,651 --> 00:11:17,288
Yes!

152
00:11:20,454 --> 00:11:21,830
I got it.

153
00:11:21,830 --> 00:11:24,439
You must be a man of your word.

154
00:11:26,078 --> 00:11:29,853
That goes for you too, don't eat your own words.

155
00:11:44,785 --> 00:11:48,647
She appears to be very cute, but she actually looks quite weird.

156
00:11:48,647 --> 00:11:50,336
You're absolutely right.

157
00:11:50,336 --> 00:11:52,748
Don't tell me your fashion tastes are the same as mine?

158
00:11:52,748 --> 00:11:56,392
Back in my younger days, I used to dress up just like her.

159
00:12:00,361 --> 00:12:02,257
Next we have...

160
00:12:02,257 --> 00:12:07,213
Also from Eitoku High... Makino Tsukushi-chan.

161
00:12:09,198 --> 00:12:10,603
What on earth is she wearing?

162
00:12:10,603 --> 00:12:13,190
It seems like she purposely cut up her clothes for that.

163
00:12:13,925 --> 00:12:17,572
Is she counting on that to impress the judges?

164
00:12:17,572 --> 00:12:23,542
She's guaranteed to be knocked out, dressing in those clothes.

165
00:12:23,543 --> 00:12:25,656
Not bad, Makino.

166
00:12:25,656 --> 00:12:27,496
That's very ingenious of you.

167
00:12:31,069 --> 00:12:35,625
It seems like the world renowned designer has something to say.

168
00:12:43,983 --> 00:12:45,530
What is he saying?

169
00:12:45,530 --> 00:12:47,588
He seems very upset.

170
00:12:47,588 --> 00:12:49,983
Nope. He's praising her.

171
00:12:49,983 --> 00:12:51,284
It's magnificent!!

172
00:12:51,284 --> 00:12:55,153
Fantastic! This is the design I've always been dreaming of.

173
00:12:58,659 --> 00:13:00,596
Makino Tsukushi-san from Eitoku High

174
00:13:00,596 --> 00:13:02,834
