530
00:42:29,973 --> 00:42:31,033
Here...

531
00:42:33,329 --> 00:42:37,583
Have you suddenly decided to give up on Makino?

532
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:39,979
Why should I give her up?

533
00:42:39,979 --> 00:42:42,741
Then what is it?

534
00:42:42,741 --> 00:42:44,534
