553
00:44:35,296 --> 00:44:37,226
An agreement?

554
00:44:37,226 --> 00:44:45,000
If that girl doesn't win the competition, you will have to
come to New York to study Management Economics.

555
00:44:44,995 --> 00:44:46,690
Management Economics?

556
00:44:46,690 --> 00:44:49,333
It lasts for 3 years.

557
00:44:50,494 --> 00:44:57,125
Even if Makino Tsukushi doesn't win,
but you agree to this condition,

558
00:44:57,105 --> 00:45:01,875
I will restore back to Makino her family status,
as well as the Confectionary Shop.

559
00:45:03,943 --> 00:45:12,250
This way, even if she doesn't win,
there is still a chance to help her.

560
00:45:15,508 --> 00:45:21,667
I think he firmly believed that you would win,
so he agreed to the conditions.

561
00:45:23,011 --> 00:45:27,344
He'll be waiting for you at
the hangar for his private jet this evening.

562
00:45:38,645 --> 00:45:42,726
I'm so stupid.

563
00:45:45,170 --> 00:45:50,034
I didn't know a thing myself, and yet I've been celebrating.

564
00:45:51,775 --> 00:45:56,047
Can you accompany me for the rest of the day?

565
00:45:56,535 --> 00:46:01,292
The last time, I went out with you when
you were feeling down.

566
00:46:02,972 --> 00:46:07,250
So, can you go out with me today?

567
00:46:09,067 --> 00:46:11,180
Is that fine with you?

568
00:46:16,018 --> 00:46:20,917
He just ran off like that.
There's nothing much I can do.

569
00:46:24,213 --> 00:46:26,021
Aren't you going to go after him?

570
00:46:27,120 --> 00:46:31,898
If you truly love him, you'd go
after him no matter where he went.

571
00:46:31,898 --> 00:46:38,750
