standing to one side and watching him leave?

572
00:46:40,898 --> 00:46:43,091
That...

573
00:46:43,594 --> 00:46:49,125
Don't you remember? Somene said this to me...

574
00:46:53,211 --> 00:46:57,861
In the end, you must always show your true feelings.

575
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:06,061
This car is from my home. Just tell the driver
where you want to go, and he'll take you there.

576
00:47:06,061 --> 00:47:07,554
Quickly go after him.

577
00:47:15,015 --> 00:47:16,782
Good luck!

578
00:47:44,186 --> 00:47:45,782
Long time no see.

579
00:47:46,549 --> 00:47:48,225
Why?

580
00:47:48,225 --> 00:47:50,045
Where's your fiance?

581
00:47:50,045 --> 00:47:55,083
I wanted to spend this Christmas
with the one I truly love.

582
00:48:07,904 --> 00:48:13,686
Why does everyone tell me to say my true feelings?

583
00:48:15,628 --> 00:48:17,630
To Makino.

584
00:48:18,348 --> 00:48:20,094
How are you?

585
00:48:20,094 --> 00:48:22,555
I'm doing fine.

586
00:48:22,956 --> 00:48:28,958
My going to New York is a bit sudden,
but I'm going there to study Management Economics.

587
00:48:28,973 --> 00:48:34,375
I'm that heir to the world famous Domyoji family,
that's why I don't have a choice.

588
00:48:34,374 --> 00:48:40,000
Initially, I thought that you were just a wild girl.

589
00:48:40,005 --> 00:48:42,669
But then, unknowingly, I started to like you.

590
00:48:42,669 --> 00:48:44,968
Don't be so full of yourself.

591
00:48:44,968 --> 00:48:49,708
Or maybe the first time I met you,
I had already taken a liking of you,

592
00:48:49,727 --> 00:48:51,932
although I gave you the Red Paper, and bullied you a lot.

593
00:48:51,932 --> 00:48:54,659
1 hundred million yen.
That's how much what you're wearing costs.

594
00:48:54,659 --> 00:48:55,698
1 hundred million?!

595
00:48:55,698 --> 00:48:58,857
You caringly took care of me in the elevator.

596
00:48:58,857 --> 00:49:00,627
Poor commoners like me are used to the cold.

597
00:49:00,627 --> 00:49:02,098
That's when I realised that you were
a gentle, warm-hearted girl.

598
00:49:02,098 --> 00:49:05,266
That's because, I, Tsukushi, am a weed.
(Tsukushi is a type of plant, horsetail)

599
00:49:06,532 --> 00:49:09,574
When I was getting beat up by Sanjyo Sakurako's men,

600
00:49:09,574 --> 00:49:12,840
it was the first time I was beat up so badly.

601
00:49:12,840 --> 00:49:19,625
It's because of you, that I found out
how much it hurts to get beaten up.

602
00:49:19,633 --> 00:49:21,268
I love you.

603
00:49:24,828 --> 00:49:29,125
When Rui returned, I thought you liked Rui instead.

604
00:49:29,133 --> 00:49:31,478
That's why I thought both of you had a relationship going.

605
00:49:31,478 --> 00:49:34,528
