607
00:49:38,936 --> 00:49:42,379
You don't know how to do anything,
and you're poor too.

608
00:49:42,379 --> 00:49:44,539
No one was able to teach you anything.

609
00:49:45,364 --> 00:49:50,521
And I didn't expect that winning TOJ
would become my responsibility.

610
00:49:50,521 --> 00:49:54,125
But, you're the best.

611
00:49:54,106 --> 00:49:56,698
You can't expect less from my girl.

612
00:49:57,791 --> 00:50:03,833
It was a pity that I wasn't able to show you the actual Saturn.

613
00:50:03,822 --> 00:50:08,021
If you and I went to the stars, we'd be aliens from Saturn.

614
00:50:08,021 --> 00:50:14,959
Perhaps the happy times, and sad times,
are all decided by fate.

615
00:50:16,747 --> 00:50:21,785
That's that's why I've decided to send you Saturn as a gift.

616
00:50:23,484 --> 00:50:28,667
Let's go to the stars, Saturnian.

617
00:50:28,667 --> 00:50:32,058
This is the first time I'm giving a gift to a girl,

618
00:50:32,058 --> 00:50:34,248
